\subsection{a}
\label{sec:orge7e7796}
\begin{center}
\includegraphics[width=.9\linewidth]{./p2_a.png}
\end{center}
\begin{itemize}
\item Here's the error vs deltax for the direct solver. The slopes about 0.75 so the error goes as \(\Delta x^{3/4}\)
\item I used Julia's built in inverse but marked the matrix as a banded matrix so it was quite fast.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{b}
